      "role": "user",
      "content": "i guess. it just doesnt feel like growth though. it feels more like... a conclusion. like when you reach the edge of the world and realize the journey was just a loop. i'm just so tired of walking. i feel like i've packed my bags and i'm just waiting for the final departure.",
